{"id":"dregs","term":"Dregs","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 75:8\">Ps. 75:8</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 51:17\">Isa. 51:17</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 51:22\">22</a>), the lees of wine which settle at the bottom of the vessel.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Psalms 75:8","Isaiah 51:17","Isaiah 51:22"]}